title: Trump pleads not guilty in Miami court over classified documents case
description: Donald Trump has pleaded not guilty to charges that he unlawfully kept national security documents when he left office and lied to officials trying to recover them.

title: At least 100 people killed after boat capsizes in Nigeria
description: At least 100 people have been killed after a boat capsized in northern Nigeria, police have said.

title: Florida is 'Trump country' and it doesn't seem that any indictment is going to change that
description: Some, perhaps, may not be aware, but the state of Florida is considered "Trump country".

title: Ukraine 'probing Russian defences' looking for weak point to send in tanks - military expert
description: Ukrainian forces are probing Russian defences along the frontline as they prepare to commit their new NATO-standard tanks to the fray.

title: Eat, Pray, Love author delays novel after criticism from Ukrainians
description: The author of the hit novel Eat, Pray, Love has announced she is delaying publication of her latest book following criticism from Ukrainian readers as it is set in Russia.

title: What happens to Silvio Berlusconi's business empire now he has gone?
description: Silvio Berlusconi, Italy's longest-serving post-war prime minister, is dead and, as a key player in the country's ruling coalition until his passing, there is much debate over what it means for Italian politics.

title: Helicopter 'mishap' leaves 22 US service personnel injured in Syria
description: A helicopter "mishap" in northeastern Syria left 22 American service personnel injured over the weekend, the US military has said.

title: 'Absolutely disgusting': Nazi protesters wave swastika flags outside Disney World
description: A group of Nazi protesters have been condemned after they waved giant swastika flags outside Disney World in Florida.

title: Woman who was declared dead knocks on her coffin at funeral
description: Funerals are more often than not a sad and sombre affair where grieving people say goodbye to a much-loved friend or relative who has died.

title: Driver was going 'too quick' in fatal wedding bus crash
description: A bus driver was driving too fast when the vehicle crashed in Australia, killing 10 wedding guests and injuring 25 others, police have alleged.
